388
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko u dalje u tom trenutku u piramidalnoj šemu ima novca?

389
00:33:58,420 --> 00:34:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] Nula. Nula. Nema ničega.

390
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:03,880
